description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 3 of 4 of the live May match up between The Dragons and The Goddesses.
With 49 seconds left the Goddesses take the lead, after being down 125pts after round one they fought back like nothing we have seen before to move ahead by 6pts. With 11 seconds left can blue hang on to come from behind and win this? Is this the upset of the year? Only one way to find out...
title: ROUND THREE: The Dragons (1-0) vs The Goddesses (0-1)
